plot marker genes

types of plots:
1. tsne colored by gene expression (input: [group, gene, +/-])
2. tsne colored by correlation (input: [genes x cells], [group, cell])
3. heatmap colored by gene expression (input: [group, gene, +/-], [clusters])
4. heatmap colored by correlation (input: [genes x cells], [clusters])

input arguments:
--genes
--matrix
--tsne
--hmap
--clust
--ident
